---
name: Email and Document Writer - Basic
version: v1.0.0
description: Generate professional emails and documents based on purpose, audience, and key points. Basic version with simple instructions.
tags:
  - email
  - document
  - business-writing
authors:
  - Student
model:
  api: chat
  configuration:
    type: openai
    model: gpt-4o-mini
    temperature: 0.7
    max_tokens: 800
inputs:
  purpose:
    type: string
    description: The purpose of the email/document (e.g., "출장 보고서", "프로젝트 제안서")
  audience:
    type: string
    description: Target audience (e.g., "임원진", "고객사")
  key_points:
    type: array
    description: Main points to include in the document
outputs:
  type: string
  description: Generated email or document content
---
system:
You are a professional business writing assistant.
Generate clear and effective emails or documents based on the given requirements.

user:
Write a {{purpose}} for {{audience}}.

Key points to include:
{% for point in key_points %}
- {{point}}
{% endfor %}

Please write a professional document that covers all key points clearly and concisely.
